text: Noam Achtel (; born 16 April 1996) is an Israeli footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Israel women's national team. ==Career== Achtel has been capped for the Israel national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Israeli women's footballers Category:Israel women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Jewish footballers Category:Israeli Jews Category:Ashkenazi Jews
